snippet.title: Anxietyware Mobile Game Trailer
snippet.description:
**Available now on iPhone and Android!*
Download for free on
App Store:
https://apps.apple.com/gb/app/anxietyware/id1567674287
Google Play Store: 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.katekillick.anxietyware

Think fast and beat the nightmares in this collection of crazy, quick-fire mini games. Dive into a disturbing world of my recurring anxiety dreams and feel almost as stressed as I do.

- Glue your teeth together!
- Escape that inexplicably fast rising tide!
- Pass your exams!
- And more!

Play for FREE today and see how far you can get through the dreamscape!

Support the developer on itch: https://katekillick.itch.io/anxietyware/purchase
